Package: psr
Type: Package
Title: Functions for Analyzing Performance Science Data 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alan Huebner, Thomas McGinn, and Matthew Sisk
Maintainer: Thomas McGinn <tmcginn1@nd.edu>
Description: This package contains functions to compute statistics relevant to performance scientists, coaches, and athletes. The functions within the package that report group-wide statistics have to do with measurement instrument reliability and individual change of athletes. There are also functions that apply a particular statistical concept to each measurement in the data.
